      "title": "代码示例 1",
      "code": "import numpy as np\ndef min_max_normalize(scores):\n    \"\"\"Min-Max 归一化到 [0, 1]\"\"\"\n    min_s = min(scores)\n    max_s = max(scores)\n    if max_s == min_s:\n        return [0.5] * len(scores)  # 避免除零\n    return [(s - min_s) / (max_s - min_s) for s in scores]\ndef linear_combination_fusion(results_list, weights=None):\n    \"\"\"\n    results_list: 列表的列表，每个内列表是 [(doc_id, score), ...]\n    weights: 检索器权重列表，默认等权\n    M = len(results_list)\n    if weights is None:\n        weights = [1.0 / M] * M\n    \n    # 构建文档到分数的映射\n    doc_scores = {}\n    for i, results in enumerate(results_list):\n        # 提取当前检索器的分数并归一化\n        doc_ids = [r[0] for r in results]\n        raw_scores = [r[1] for r in results]\n        norm_scores = min_max_normalize(raw_scores)\n        \n        for doc_id, norm_score in zip(doc_ids, norm_scores):\n            if doc_id not in doc_scores:\n                doc_scores[doc_id] = 0.0\n            doc_scores[doc_id] += weights[i] * norm_score\n    # 按融合分数降序排序\n    sorted_docs = sorted(doc_scores.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)\n    return sorted_docs\n# 示例使用\nretriever1 = [(\"doc1\", 8.2), (\"doc2\", 7.5), (\"doc3\", 6.1)]\nretriever2 = [(\"doc4\", 0.92), (\"doc2\", 0.88), (\"doc5\", 0.85)]\nfused = linear_combination_fusion([retriever1, retriever2])\nprint(\"加权求和融合结果:\", fused)",
