      "title": "代码示例 4",
      "code": "def zeropower_via_newtonschulz5(G, steps=5):\n    \"\"\"Newton-Schulz 迭代计算 G @ (G^T G)^(-1/2)\"\"\"\n    assert len(G.shape) == 2\n    a, b, c = (3.4445, -4.7750, 2.0315)\n    X = G.bfloat16()\n    if G.size(0) > G.size(1):\n        X = X.T\n    X = X / (X.norm() + 1e-7)\n    for _ in range(steps):\n        A = X @ X.T\n        B = b * A + c * A @ A\n        X = a * X + B @ X\n    if G.size(0) > G.size(1):\n        X = X.T\n    return X",
