        "title": "代码示例 1",
        "code": "# 文件: dpo_train.py\n# 依赖: pip install trl transformers peft datasets accelerate\nimport torch\nfrom datasets import load_dataset\nfrom transformers import AutoModelForCausalLM, AutoTokenizer\nfrom trl import DPOTrainer, DPOConfig\nfrom peft import LoraConfig\n\n# 1. 加载 SFT 后基座 (SFT 步骤见 L55)\nmodel = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(\"./qwen2-7b-sft\", torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16)\nref_model = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(\"./qwen2-7b-sft\", torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16)\ntokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(\"./qwen2-7b-sft\")\nif tokenizer.pad_token is None: tokenizer.pad_token = tokenizer.eos_token\n\n# 2. 偏好数据 (UltraFeedback / Anthropic HH-RLHF)\ndataset = load_dataset(\"HuggingFaceH4/ultrafeedback_binarized\", split=\"train_prefs[:10000]\")\ndef to_dpo(ex):\n    return {\"prompt\": ex[\"prompt\"],\n            \"chosen\": ex[\"chosen\"][-1][\"content\"],\n            \"rejected\": ex[\"rejected\"][-1][\"content\"]}\ndataset = dataset.map(to_dpo, remove_columns=dataset.column_names)\n\n# 3. DPO 配置 (LoRA 节省显存)\nlora_config = LoraConfig(r=16, lora_alpha=32,\n    target_modules=[\"q_proj\",\"k_proj\",\"v_proj\",\"o_proj\"], task_type=\"CAUSAL_LM\")\nconfig = DPOConfig(\n    output_dir=\"./qwen2-7b-dpo\",\n    num_train_epochs=2,\n    per_device_train_batch_size=2, gradient_accumulation_steps=8,\n    learning_rate=5e-7, bf16=True,\n    beta=0.1,                        # DPO 关键超参\n    max_length=1024, max_prompt_length=512,\n    loss_type=\"sigmoid\",             # 标准 DPO loss\n    logging_steps=20, save_steps=500,\n)\n\ntrainer = DPOTrainer(\n    model=model, ref_model=ref_model,\n    args=config, train_dataset=dataset,\n    processing_class=tokenizer, peft_config=lora_config,\n)\ntrainer.train()",
        "language": "python",
        "repo": "None",
        "install_cmd": "pip install openai transformers"
