        "title": "代码示例 3",
        "code": "# 文件: simpo_train.py\n# SimPO 核心: 不需要 ref_model + 长度归一化\nimport torch\nfrom datasets import load_dataset\nfrom transformers import AutoModelForCausalLM, AutoTokenizer\nfrom trl import CPOTrainer, CPOConfig  # SimPO 在 trl 0.9+ 用 CPO + loss_type=simpo\n\nmodel = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(\"./qwen2-7b-sft\", torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16)\ntokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(\"./qwen2-7b-sft\")\n\ndataset = load_dataset(\"HuggingFaceH4/ultrafeedback_binarized\", split=\"train_prefs[:5000]\")\n\nconfig = CPOConfig(\n    output_dir=\"./qwen2-7b-simpo\",\n    num_train_epochs=2,\n    per_device_train_batch_size=2, gradient_accumulation_steps=8,\n    learning_rate=1e-6, bf16=True,\n    loss_type=\"simpo\",                # 关键: 切换为 SimPO\n    beta=2.0,                          # SimPO beta 通常 2-10, 远大于 DPO\n    cpo_alpha=0.0,                     # 关闭 SFT 损失\n    max_length=1024, max_prompt_length=512,\n)\n# SimPO 不需要 ref_model 参数\ntrainer = CPOTrainer(\n    model=model,\n    args=config, train_dataset=dataset.map(lambda x: {\n        \"prompt\": x[\"prompt\"], \"chosen\": x[\"chosen\"][-1][\"content\"],\n        \"rejected\": x[\"rejected\"][-1][\"content\"]}),\n    processing_class=tokenizer,\n)\ntrainer.train()",
